<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFPingree1998"><a href="/wiki/David_Pingree" title="David Pingree">Pingree, David</a> (1998), "Legacies in Astronomy and Celestial Omens", in Dalley, Stephanie, <i>The Legacy of Mesopotamia</i>, Oxford University Press, pp.&#160;125 – 137, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198149468" class="internal">ISBN 0198149468</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Legacies+in+Astronomy+and+Celestial+Omens&amp;rft.atitle=The+Legacy+of+Mesopotamia&amp;rft.aulast=Pingree&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft.au=Pingree%2C+David&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B125+%E2%80%93+137&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0198149468&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:History_of_astronomy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRochberg2004">Rochberg, Francesca (2004), <i>The Heavenly Writing: Divination, Horoscopy, and Astronomy in Mesopotamian Culture</i>, Cambridge University Press</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Heavenly+Writing%3A+Divination%2C+Horoscopy%2C+and+Astronomy+in+Mesopotamian+Culture&amp;rft.aulast=Rochberg&amp;rft.aufirst=Francesca&amp;rft.au=Rochberg%2C+Francesca&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:History_of_astronomy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li>Stephenson, Bruce. <i>Kepler's Physical Astronomy</i>, Studies in the History of Mathematics and Physical Sciences, 13. New York: Springer, 1987 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0387965416" class="internal">ISBN 0-387-96541-6</a></li>
<li>Walker, Christopher (ed.). <i>Astronomy before the telescope</i>. British Museum Press 1996 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0714117463" class="internal">ISBN 0-7141-1746-3</a></li>
</ul>
